Act No. 2 (H.35). An act relating to unmerging the individual and small group health
insurance markets
Subjects: Health; health insurance; Vermont Health Benefit Exchange; unmerged
markets
This act permanently unmerges the individual and small group health insurance
markets, which had been temporarily unmerged on a one- or two-year basis since 2022.
The act also repeals outdated language regarding implementation of the Vermont Health
Benefit Exchange.
Effective Date: January 1, 2026
